Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public static interface Remote.ToIntFunction<T> extends ToIntFunction<T>, Serializable
Represents a function that produces an int-valued result. This is the int-producing primitive specialization for Remote.Function.

This is a functional interface whose functional method is ToIntFunction.applyAsInt(Object).
